WEBVTT

1
00:35:01.350 --> 00:35:02.940 
-不是戒指吗  -什么
- No ring? - What?

2
00:35:02.980 --> 00:35:05.970 
不是  但在盒子里
No, but inside that box...

3
00:35:06.020 --> 00:35:07.680 
在这些纸片的下面
...underneath all that crap...

4
00:35:07.720 --> 00:35:09.980 
有张手写的纸条
...there was a little handwritten note...

5
00:35:10.020 --> 00:35:13.550 
上面写着  酒店的地址  约会的时间
With the address to a hotel, date, and time.

6
00:35:13.590 --> 00:35:15.290 
很汉弗里·博加特风格的做事方式
Real humphrey bogart-type stuff.

7
00:35:15.330 --> 00:35:16.690 
是的
Yeah.

8
00:35:16.730 --> 00:35:18.560 
非常阳刚
Masculine.

9
00:35:18.600 --> 00:35:20.460 
不管怎样  很自然  马格瑞特以为
Anyway, naturally, margaret thought...

10
00:35:20.500 --> 00:35:22.060 
我以为他在和别人约会
I thought he was seeing someone else.

11
00:35:22.100 --> 00:35:24.230 
那时我感觉太糟糕了
It was a terrible time for me,

12
00:35:24.270 --> 00:35:26.640 
但我还是去了那家酒店
But I went to that hotel anyway.

13
00:35:26.670 --> 00:35:28.770 
到了那  我很用力地敲门
I went there and I pounded on the door,

14
00:35:28.810 --> 00:35:30.640 
可是门根本没锁上
But the door was already unlocked.

15
00:35:30.680 --> 00:35:34.540 
当我推打开门  他就
And as swung open that door, there he was...

